These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, quad-bike, trike
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the train##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | trike | bus | train | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, baking, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | singing | sudoku | puzzles | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, police-officer, journalist
1. the fisherman is on the right of the police-officer##1
2. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
3. the firefighter is the firefighter##1
4. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | journalist | firefighter | police-officer | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, filmmaking, rock-climbing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | fishing | filmmaking | rock-climbing | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, superhero, martial-arts, spy
1. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | superhero | spy | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, singing, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | singing | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, colombian, japanese
1. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
3. the thai is between the malaysian and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | colombian | malaysian | thai | japanese |

