.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, airplane, bus
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | scooter | bus | ship | airplane |

