3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | video-games | skydiving | card-games |

