.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, pony, frog
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the horse##2
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | mouse | horse | pony |

